<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html lang=zh-tw ng-app="ngAboutUs">
	<head>
		<meta charset=utf-8>
		<title>About Us</title>
		<meta name="keywords" content="">
		<meta name="description" content="">
		<meta http-equiv="pragma" content="no-cache">
		<meta http-equiv="expires" content="0">
		<meta name="generator" content="Editplus ">
		<meta name="author" content="">
		<meta name="robots" content="">
		<meta name="copyright" content=""> 
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/aboutus/style.css">
		<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
		<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.1.5/angular.min.js"></script>
		<script  src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.2.0-rc.2/angular-route.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="https://code.angularjs.org/1.3.9/angular-mocks.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="js/course/angular-animate.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="js/aboutus/ngAboutUs.js"></script>
	</head>
	<body ng-controller="aboutUsCtrl" >
		<% include ../shared/navbar.ejs %>
		<div class="frame" ng-show="currentPage === 1 && !showContent" ng-class="{'frame-load':!showContent; 'change': director}">
			<div class="circleCenter" ng-click="spreadChild('both')" ng-class="{'clicked' : (isActivatedLeft && isActivatedRight) }"></div>
			<div class="secondLayer">
				<div class="circleFirstChildLeft" ng-click="spreadChild('left')" ng-class="{'clicked' : isActivatedLeft}" $event.stopPropagation();> 
					<div class="thirdChild-1" ng-class="{'isActivatedLeft-1' : isActivatedLeft}" ng-click="flip('TD'); spreadChild('stay');" $event.stopPropagation();>
					</div>	
					<div class="thirdChild-2" ng-class="{'isActivatedLeft-2' : isActivatedLeft}" ng-click="flip('CD'); spreadChild('stay');" $event.stopPropagation();>
					</div>	
					<div class="thirdChild-3" ng-class="{'isActivatedLeft-3' : isActivatedLeft}" ng-click="flip('HR'); spreadChild('stay');" $event.stopPropagation();>
					</div>	
					<div class="thirdChild-4" ng-class="{'isActivatedLeft-4' : isActivatedLeft}" ng-click="flip('BD'); spreadChild('stay');" $event.stopPropagation();>
					</div>	
					<div class="thirdChild-5" ng-class="{'isActivatedLeft-5' : isActivatedLeft}" ng-click="flip('DM'); spreadChild('stay'); boom=true;" $event.stopPropagation();>
					</div>	
				</div>
				<div class="circleFirstChildRight" ng-click="spreadChild('right')" ng-class="{'clicked' : isActivatedRight}">
					<div class="thirdChild-1" ng-class="{'isActivatedRight-1' : isActivatedRight}" ng-click="flip('HC'); spreadChild('stay');" $event.stopPropagation();></div>	
					<div class="thirdChild-2" ng-class="{'isActivatedRight-2' : isActivatedRight}" ng-click="flip('Course'); spreadChild('stay');" $event.stopPropagation();></div>	
					<div class="thirdChild-3" ng-class="{'isActivatedRight-3' : isActivatedRight}" ng-click="flip('CR'); spreadChild('stay');" $event.stopPropagation();></div>
					<div class="thirdChild-4" ng-class="{'isActivatedRight-4' : isActivatedRight}" ng-click="flip('HackCampus'); spreadChild('stay');" $event.stopPropagation();></div>
				</div>
				
			</div>
			<div class="nextPage" ng-click="nextPage(currentPage);">
				<i class="fa fa-angle-double-down fa-4x" ></i>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="content" ng-show="showContent" ng-class="{'content-activated':showContent}">
			<div class="closeBtn" ng-click="showContent = !showContent">
				<i class="fa fa-4x fa-chevron-circle-left"></i>
			</div>
			<div class="header">{{title}}</div>
			<!-- <div class="header">
				<img src="imgs/aboutus/TD_.svg">
			</div> -->
			<div class="member">
				<div class="memberBlock" ng-repeat="member in members">
					<div class="picture" style="background:url({{member.url}})"></div>
					<div class="name">{{member.name}}</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="director" ng-show="currentPage === 2;" >
			<div class="prevPage" ng-click="prevPage(currentPage)">
				<i class="fa fa-angle-double-up fa-4x"></i>
			</div>
			<div class="content">
				<h1>HackNTU 臺大黑客松</h1>
				<div class="photo" style="background:url('https://graph.facebook.com/s3355004/picture?width=300')"> 
					<p>總召／李冠憶</p>
				</div>
				<div class="photo" style="background:url('../../imgs/aboutus/member/TD_陳步青.jpg')"> 
					<p>技術副召／陳步青</p>
				</div>
				<div class="photo" style="background:url('../../imgs/aboutus/member/DM_黃偉軒.jpg')"> 
					<p>行銷副召／黃偉軒</p>
				</div>
				<div style="height: 50px;"></div>
				<h1>Hacker spirit</h1>
				<p>
				獨⽴思考，⾃由探索，發揮創意，解決問題 <br>
				The spirit represents thinking independently, discovering questions and
				solving them with creativity.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="nextPage" ng-click="nextPage(currentPage)">
				<i class="fa fa-angle-double-down fa-4x"></i>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="director" ng-show="currentPage === 3;" >
			<div class="prevPage" ng-click="prevPage(currentPage)" ng-show="currentPage > 1">
				<i class="fa fa-angle-double-up fa-4x"></i>
			</div>
			<div class="content">
				<h1>起源</h1>
				<p>
				Hackathon為近年來⾵⾏於國內外知名企業以及⼀流⼤學間的創意發想與
				實踐活動。 <br>	
				然⽽，包括台⼤在內，台灣各⼤專院校卻都沒有提供類似的平台或是活動，
				能讓創意萌芽、發展。<br>
				HackNTU共同創辦⼈之⼀的張凱迪，在參加 Yahoo的Hackday之後，深刻意識到這個問題。因此，憑藉著對⿊客精神的熱愛與使命感，2013年，在台⼤正式成⽴HackNTU 。
				</p>
				<br>
				<h1>Origin</h1>
				<p>
				Hackathon is a popular event in recent years. Both domestic and foreign
				enterprises, and prestigious universities hold such event to promote the
				spirit of creative thinking and practicing.
				However, all universities in Taiwan, including NTU, didn’t have such
				event.
				KD Chang, one of the co-founders of HackNTU, determined to started a
				hackathon in NTU after he participated the Hackday held by Yahoo.
				In the year of 2013, HackNTU was established.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="nextPage" ng-click="nextPage(currentPage)" ng-show="currentPage < maxPage">
				<i class="fa fa-angle-double-down fa-4x"></i>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="director" ng-show="currentPage === 4;" >
			<div class="prevPage" ng-click="prevPage(currentPage)" ng-show="currentPage > 1">
				<i class="fa fa-angle-double-up fa-4x"></i>
			</div>
			<div class="content">
				<h1>什麼是黑客松？</h1>
				<p>
				Hackathon = Hack + Marathon <br>
				Hack 的原意是解決問題、創意程式設計，⽽⾮蓄意破壞或竊取機密⽂件。
				</p>
				<h1>What is Hackathon?</h1>
				<p>
				Hackathon= Hack+ Marathon <br>
				Hack originally means to solve problems and design creative programs. It
				does not mean to destroy or steal confidential documents.
				</p>
				<br>
				<h1>編程 X 設計 X 食物</h1>
				<p>
				由三⾄五⼈組成團隊，在數天的活動期間，提出⽣活中注意到的問題與解決⽅
				法，並透過技術執⾏，創造出有⽤⽽創新的產品。
				</p>
				
				<h1>Code X Design X Food</h1>
				<p>
				The goal of Hackathon is to discover problems and design a way to solve it. It
				typically last between a day to a week, developing products by a team with
				3-5 programmers, including graphic designers, interface designers and
				project managers.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="nextPage" ng-click="nextPage(currentPage)" ng-show="currentPage < maxPage">
				<i class="fa fa-angle-double-down fa-4x"></i>
			</div>
		</div>

